---
const phone = '+33 1 42 36 58 90';
const phoneHref = 'tel:+33142365890';
---

<section class="bg-[#C9A99A] py-16">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-white/80 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Disponible du lundi au samedi</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Variable', Georgia, serif; font-weight: 600;">
      Offrez-vous un moment rien que pour vous
    </h2>
    <p class="text-white/85 mb-8 text-lg">Un soin, un massage, une parenthèse de douceur. On vous attend.</p>
    <a
      href={phoneHref}
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white text-[#C9A99A] hover:bg-[#FAF7F5] font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors duration-200 text-lg"
    >
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.49 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.4 1h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.91 8.37a16 16 0 0 0 5.72 5.72l1.83-1.84a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 14.92z"/></svg>
      {phone}
    </a>
    <p class="mt-4 text-white/70 text-sm">Réponse en moins de 2h · Sans engagement</p>
  </div>
</section>
